<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1598</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ( wklạmk ḥbynạh fy qlwbnạ kẖbynạh )2
 ( dh ktạb mn rwḥ ạllh dh rsạlẗ ạ̹bn ạllh )2
 2- ( fy klạmk sẖwfnạ ṣlyb sẖkẖṣ yswʿ ạlḥbyb )2
 ( ạ̹ʿlạn ʿn ḥb ʿjyb frḥẗ lkl ạlkẖṭạẗ )2
 3- ( wqrynạ ạlmʿjzạt ạ̉mwạt tḥyạ fy lḥẓạt )2
 ( nsạnạ ḥb ạldẖạt ldẖtnạ klạm ạllh )2
 4- ( wrjạl sẖhdwạ bạ̹ymạn wktạbnạ byhm mlyạn )2
 ( nḥtạj m ạlwqt zmạn lw qlnạ rjạl ạllh )2
 5- ( qạlnạ ṣkẖr ạldhwr dh ktạb kl ạlʿṣwr )2
 ( ạlsmạ wạlạ̉rḍ tzwl wạlklmẗ dy bạqyẗ mʿạk )2
 6- ( byqwlwạ ḥrfnạh mạsẖạfwsẖ yswʿ jwạh )2
 ( dh ạlḥy wạ̹smh ḥyạẗ ạ̹ṣḥwạ dh klạm ạllh )2</lyrics>
<title>klạmk ḥbnạh</title>
</song>